{"tid":1586629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗稱暴力衝突或令小朋友仇恨某類人 籲優先考慮兒童利益","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T06:32:49.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c3fc5f7075cc2cfc95a6af6dd384a43e85c659","tid":1586629,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190922/large/1569121665_b32a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190922%2Flarge%2F1569121665_b32a.jpg&h=439e2d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張建宗指暴力衝突可能令兒童出現創傷後壓力症徵狀，或對某類人產生不信任或仇恨。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n反修例引起的警民衝突持續，政務司司長張建宗發表網誌表示，自己過去一段時間已默默展開與不同界別人士的深度對話。他稱，兒童事務委員會舉行茶會時，委員都擔心事態發展令兒童身心和精神受影響。有家長和帶同子女參與遊行示威，即使他們沒有直接參與，亦很大機會從新聞或社交媒體接觸大量衝突和暴力片段，令他們感到害怕及迷惘，亦可能出現創傷後壓力症徵狀，甚至有兒童模仿暴力行為，或對某類人產生不信任或仇恨，為害極之深遠。張表示，成年人有責任守護孩子，呼籲大眾一切以兒童最佳利益為優先考慮。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府周四（26日）在灣仔伊館舉行的首場社區對話，名額僅150人，首日網上報名已超額逾80倍。但張建宗強調，行政長官及問責團隊希望與社會各階層、不同政治立場和背景的人士展開真誠、深入對話，讓政府更徹底了解社會深層次問題，尋求解決方案，取代對立，重建互信。<br />\n<br />\n而提到下月發表的《施政報告》，張建宗重申，政府銳意堅攻房屋及土地供應問題，有關方面將是新一份報告重點之一。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局長羅致光亦發表網誌，指雖然在目前的政治氣候，有人可能會譏諷政府無論說甚麼、做甚麼，年輕一代都不會領情，但他並不那麼悲觀。他解釋，最近在大小不同場合，包括關愛基金簡介會或與各個為民請命的壓力團體會面，所接觸到的年輕朋友和前線社工，都能夠就各項社會實務議題和平理性地討論和提出建議，彼此都能夠坦誠溝通。羅致光期望，能更深入聽取青年人和社會大眾的聲音，讓各項民生政策可以更到位，強調對話一定比對抗好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190922/60071202?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F60071202%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=dce45255\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190922%2F60071202%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6020dec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190922/60071202?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5e2e2d9f4e2f51b9b84658b227ec54174f5fbdff","tid":1586629,"uid":87780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"應該培養愛國愛黨精神<br />\n幫你講埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c56d99b04da912df568bec16dc833097d694e3","tid":1586629,"uid":29784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"而家後生就犯法啦"},{"pid":"be1da6b9fca78fd45fc6c7a4f24912ebedb179e7","tid":1586629,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"最好箍埋個監視腦電腦箍<br />\n同支那無縫接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03c90aff90f5c22eb9c769fdb0f14cdb71863cf","tid":1586629,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"仇恨黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8818838f0c5288fc4e6a7ede57dee8ef72d0030","tid":1586629,"uid":83992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:22:35.000Z","msg":"對某類人產生不信任或仇恨<br />\n<br />\n某類人咪黑警囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf291f08f2ae55ddea48da472c5ad1e1506e54d4","tid":1586629,"uid":221490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"琴晚拉左個10歲<br />\n張生有冇睇新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p